casebody.data:
Crystal Renee ELLENBARGER, Respondent,
v.
Shane Stanton BRANSTETTER, Appellant. WD 80468 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: January 30, 2018 William E. Shull, Liberty, MO, for respondent. Marilyn M. Shapiro, Kansas City, MO, for appellant. Before Division Four: Mark D. Pfeiffer, Chief Judge, Presiding, Cynthia L. Martin, Judge and Anthony Rex Gabbert, Judge

ORDER

Per curiam:

Shane Branstetter appeals from a judgment entering a full order of protection to Crystal Ellenbarger. Branstetter alleges error in the admission of an anonymous letter over his hearsay objection, and that entry of the full order of protection was against the weight of the evidence, not supported by substantial evidence, and misapplied the law. Finding no error, we affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
